readme:
# phnx-snippets package

Adds snippet for .phnx template for view definition file.

**Usage Info:**
- In any file, typing `phnx` will trigger the template for .phnx file automatically.
- The description for `phnx` file will by highlighed to edit by default.
- Pressing `Tab` once after above edit will next highlight the `name` attribute of phnx template to edit. `Tab` will behave normally after this point.

![A screenshot of your package](https://f.cloud.github.com/assets/69169/2290250/c35d867a-a017-11e3-86be-cd7c5bf3ff9b.gif)
